import React from 'react'
import Simple from './Components/Simple'
import appan from './Components/appan.jpg'
import lord from './Components/lord.jpg'
import muruga from './Components/muruga.jfif'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Simple name="Muruga"place="Thiruchendhur"img={appan}mantra="Om"show={true}/>
    <Simple name="Kathirvela" place="Palani"img={lord}mantra="Saravana bhava"show/>
    <Simple name="Senthil" place="Thovalai" img={muruga} mantra="Arohara"show={true}/>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
